===================================================================================
IMPORTANT NOTES ABOUT THE RESPONSE
===================================================================================

1. PHONE NUMBERS:
   - Located in: stl119:CustomerContact/stl119:Phone
   - Only numeric digits are included in the response
   - PhoneType indicates: H (Home), B (Business), M (Mobile), O (Other)
   - Typically all passengers in same PNR share same phone contact info

2. PASSENGER NAMES:
   - FirstName includes title (e.g., "JOHN MR", "JANE MRS")
   - Parse carefully if you need to separate title from actual name
   - LastName is separate field

3. SEAT INFORMATION:
   - SeatLocation shows assigned seat (e.g., "12A", "14C")
   - May be empty if seats not yet assigned

4. FLIGHT INFORMATION:
   - Included automatically in Segments section
   - Shows actual flight operated, not just what was searched for
   - May contain multiple segments per passenger

5. PAGINATION:
   - If results > 800, response will contain NumberPages > 1
   - You'll need to make additional requests to retrieve all results
   - Use TokenCriteria for pagination (advanced feature)

